822
00:56:53,440 --> 00:56:54,639
[SPEAKER_01] I optimizirali smo li to?

823
00:56:54,800 --> 00:56:55,360
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo ni blizu.

824
00:56:55,760 --> 00:56:57,199
